{"TopicId":222849,"ForumId":130,"TopicTitle":"KerbalHeadlamp [0.1.2 for KSP2 0.2.0]","CreatedByName":"WiS3","CreatedById":232120,"CreatedDateTime":"2024-01-09T11:43:36Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"WiS3","CreatedById":232120,"CreatedDateTime":"2024-01-09T11:43:36Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp style=\u0022text-align:center;\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cspan style=\u0022font-size:36px;\u0022\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003EKerbalHeadlamp\u003C/strong\u003E\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp style=\u0022text-align:center;\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u00229c4e3ab4-60c2-427e-b88a-1a007ac50d56\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 data-ratio=\u002274.34\u0022 height=\u0022533\u0022 width=\u0022717\u0022 src=\u0022https://github.com/WiS3/KerbalHeadlamp/assets/2456380/9c4e3ab4-60c2-427e-b88a-1a007ac50d56\u0022\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp style=\u0022text-align:center;\u0022\u003E\nAvailable on \u003Cstrong\u003E\u003Cabbr title=\u0022Comprehensive Kerbal Archive Network (a KSP mod manager)\u0022\u003E\u003Cabbr title=\u0022Comprehensive Kerbal Archive Network (a KSP mod manager)\u0022\u003ECKAN\u003C/abbr\u003E\u003C/abbr\u003E\u003Cbr\u003E\nSpacedock\u003C/strong\u003E:\u00A0\u00A0\u003Ca href=\u0022https://spacedock.info/mod/3540/KerbalHeadlamp\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003Ehttps://spacedock.info/mod/3540/KerbalHeadlamp\u003C/a\u003E\u003Cbr\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003ESource\u003C/strong\u003E:\u00A0\u003Ca href=\u0022https://github.com/WiS3/KerbalHeadlamp\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003Ehttps://github.com/WiS3/KerbalHeadlamp\u003C/a\u003E\u003Cbr\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003ELicense\u003C/strong\u003E: MIT\u003Cbr\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp style=\u0022text-align:center;\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cspan style=\u0022font-size:18px;\u0022\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003EDESCRIPTION:\u003C/strong\u003E\u003C/span\u003E\u003Cbr\u003E\nAdd EVA Kerbal Headlamps like in KSP1.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp style=\u0022text-align:center;\u0022\u003E\nYou can toggle them using the\u00A0\u003Cstrong\u003EVessel Action\u003C/strong\u003E\u00A0icon aswell the\u00A0\u003Cstrong\u003ELights\u003C/strong\u003E\u00A0ActionGroup (default is\u00A0\u003Cstrong\u003EU\u003C/strong\u003E\u00A0Key).\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp style=\u0022text-align:center;\u0022\u003E\nYou can also change the color of the light by expanding the advanced controls in the\u00A0\u003Cem\u003EParts Manager\u003C/em\u003E.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp style=\u0022text-align:center;\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cspan style=\u0022font-size:18px;\u0022\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003EKNOWN ISSUES:\u003C/strong\u003E\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp style=\u0022text-align:center;\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cs\u003E- If there are multiple Kerbals on EVA the light setting is shared for all of them.\u003C/s\u003E\u00A0(Fixed in 0.1.2)\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222024-01-10T09:27:34Z\u0022 title=\u002201/10/2024 09:27  AM\u0022 data-short=\u0022Jan 10\u0022\u003EJanuary 10\u003C/time\u003E by WiS3\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003Cbr\u003EUpdated to 0.1.2\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"fourfa","CreatedById":151713,"CreatedDateTime":"2024-01-09T21:48:56Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThanks for this, saw it in \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Comprehensive Kerbal Archive Network (a KSP mod manager)\u0022\u003ECKAN\u003C/abbr\u003E, loaded it, works great\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"zulu354","CreatedById":187226,"CreatedDateTime":"2024-01-20T17:24:20Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nLove it!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Mitokandria","CreatedById":222458,"CreatedDateTime":"2024-02-16T22:18:31Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nDoes the headlamp in the current version of the game not act this way? (I\u0027m sure this is a stupid question)\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"mattihase","CreatedById":73161,"CreatedDateTime":"2024-02-21T20:42:20Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00224366905\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022222849\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221708121911\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022222458\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Mitokandria\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\nOn 2/16/2024 at 10:18 PM, Mitokandria said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nDoes the headlamp in the current version of the game not act this way? (I\u0027m sure this is a stupid question)\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nUnless they added one in 0.2.1 then the headlamp isn\u0027t even in the game yet.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Deadly_Laser","CreatedById":231894,"CreatedDateTime":"2024-02-22T20:53:52Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00224366905\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022222849\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221708121911\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022222458\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Mitokandria\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\nOn 2/17/2024 at 1:18 AM, Mitokandria said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nDoes the headlamp in the current version of the game not act this way? (I\u0027m sure this is a stupid question)\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nNo, for some reason in stock KSP2 the headlamp is currently not a real light source\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"DunaColonist","CreatedById":207161,"CreatedDateTime":"2024-03-17T13:53:38Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nSimply can\u0027t live without it.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nSimple mod but litteraly a must.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI need to check in game but\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n=\u0026gt; would it make sense to have EC usage ?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n=\u0026gt; are there dead lamps in the outside of the various command pods ?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222024-03-17T14:00:13Z\u0022 title=\u002203/17/2024 02:00  PM\u0022 data-short=\u0022Mar 17\u0022\u003EMarch 17\u003C/time\u003E by DunaColonist\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"magnemoe","CreatedById":57801,"CreatedDateTime":"2024-03-19T15:32:03Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThis mod saved me in the mohole, I could not see an thing and needed to reach the other lander as the current had fallen over after landing.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"jordanjay29","CreatedById":62787,"CreatedDateTime":"2024-03-19T23:25:27Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI can\u0027t believe this isn\u0027t in the game yet, so thank you for modding it in!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nTook it to the Dark Side of the Mun and been seeing in color ever since.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"}]}